												<span class="tag-links">
					<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/aaron-swartz/" rel="tag">Aaron Swartz</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/manifesto/" rel="tag">manifesto</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/open-access/" rel="tag">open access</a>				</span>
				
