			<span class="tag-links">
<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/angryip/" rel="tag">angryip</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/apt-get/" rel="tag">apt-get</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/raspberry-pi/" rel="tag">Raspberry Pi</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/raspi-config/" rel="tag">raspi-config</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/to-do/" rel="tag">to-do</a>, <a href="http://cavebeat.org/tag/update/" rel="tag">update</a>			</span>
			<span class="sep"> | </span>
			<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://cavebeat.org/2013/08/to-do-after-install-on-raspberry-pi/#respond" title="Comment on To-Do after install on Raspberry Pi"><span class="leave-reply">Leave a reply</span></a></span>
	</div><!-- .entry-meta-icons -->
